  "prompt": "What is Yelp?",
  "response": "Yelp is a popular online platform and mobile app that connects people with local businesses. It allows users to search for, read reviews, and rate a wide variety of businesses such as restaurants, cafes, bars, shops, service providers, and more. Yelp provides detailed information, including business hours, address, phone number, photos, and menu items. Businesses can also claim their Yelp page to interact with customers, post updates, and respond to reviews. Users can contribute by writing reviews, uploading photos, and providing ratings to help others make informed decisions about local services and establishments.",
